# Implementation Plan V3 - Wireframe Integration

## Goal Description
Integrate the specific layouts from [wireframe.docx](file:///Users/viveksuyal/Documents/Wishtune/frontend/wireframe.docx) into the existing React app. This expands the site from a simple Funnel (V2) to a comprehensive Brand Experience (V3) accessible via `/shop`.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Architecture Update**:
> - **Squeeze Page (`/`)** stays as the "Cold Traffic" entry.
> - **Wireframe Landing Page** will be implemented at **`/shop`** (Acting as the Brand Home).
> - **Category Pages** (`/shop/:category`) will be added.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Brand Landing Page (`/shop`) - Wireframe Section 1
- **Hero**: "Music Designed to Shift Your Mood" (Video BG).
- **Use-Case Selector**: Cards for Sleep, Party, Shower, Personalized.
- **Feature Strip**: Studio Quality, Instant Download, Lifetime Access.

### 2. Category Page (`/shop/sleep`, etc.) - Wireframe Section 2
- **Hero**: Specific outcome text ("Fall asleep faster...").
- **Smart Product Grid**: Card with "Preview", "Duration", "Mood Tag".
- **Comparison Strip**: "Which one is right for you?" table/section.

### 3. Enhanced PDP (`/product/:id`) - Wireframe Section 3
- **Main Area**: Phone Mockup + Audio Player.
- **Audio Visualization**: [NEW] Animated waveform component.
- **Trust Section**: Reviews ("I fall asleep in 10 minutes").
- **FAQs**: Accordion section for objection handling.

### 4. Checkout & Success - Wireframe Section 4 & 5
- **Checkout**: Minimalist updates (if any).
- **Post-Purchase Upsell**: Ensure Bundle Offer logic is visible.

